query:
INSERT INTO "UserItemAccess" (
            "id",
            "user_id",
            "item_id",
            "item_type",
            "access_level",
            "granted_from_channel_id",
            "created_at",
            "updated_at"
        )
        SELECT 
            u.id, 
            u.user_id, 
            u.item_id, 
            u.item_type, 
            u.access_level::"AccessLevel", 
            u.granted_from_channel_id,
            NOW() as created_at,
            NOW() as updated_at
        FROM UNNEST(
            $1::uuid[], 
            $2::text[], 
            $3::text[], 
            $4::text[], 
            $5::text[],
            $6::uuid[]
        ) as u(
            id, 
            user_id, 
            item_id, 
            item_type, 
            access_level, 
            granted_from_channel_id
        )
        ON CONFLICT ("user_id", "item_id", "item_type", "granted_from_channel_id") 
        DO NOTHING
